by telling me that's a coincidence.

116
00:14:34,874 --> 00:14:37,274
No, it's no coincidence.

117
00:14:38,344 --> 00:14:40,039
Do I know you?

118
00:14:40,079 --> 00:14:42,070
My name is Raymond Price.

119
00:14:43,415 --> 00:14:47,613
