00:16:28,988 --> 00:16:32,116
'That's a beautiful thing,
ladies and gentlemen. '

146
00:17:38,357 --> 00:17:41,918
'The body of internationally renowned
author Anna Rivers

147
00:17:41,994 --> 00:17:46,431
